## Third-Party Licenses

This application bundles pre-compiled binaries from the following libraries.
Their source code is available at the links below.

| Library | License | Source |
|---------|---------|--------|
| SoX | LGPL 2.1+ | https://sourceforge.net/projects/sox/ |
| libsndfile | LGPL 2.1 | https://github.com/libsndfile/libsndfile |
| libFLAC | BSD 3-Clause | https://xiph.org/flac/ |
| libvorbis | BSD 3-Clause | https://xiph.org/vorbis/ |
| libogg | BSD 3-Clause | https://xiph.org/ogg/ |
| libopus | BSD 3-Clause | https://opus-codec.org/ |
| libopusfile | BSD 3-Clause | https://gitlab.xiph.org/xiph/opusfile |
| libmp3lame | LGPL 2.0 | https://lame.sourceforge.io/ |
| libmpg123 | LGPL 2.1 | https://www.mpg123.de/ |
| libmad | GPL 2.0 | https://www.underbit.com/products/mad/ |
| libpng | libpng License | http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/libpng.html |

### LGPL notice

The LGPL-licensed libraries (SoX, libsndfile, libmp3lame, libmpg123, libsndfile)
are dynamically linked. You may replace them with your own builds by rebuilding
the sox-bundle using `scripts/bundle-sox.mjs` against your preferred versions.

